criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. 18-80 years old;

          2. ECOG score 0 or 1 point;

          3. Patients with suspected or confirmed lung cancer, esophagus cancer, cervical cancer or
             other cancers who are suggested by the clinicians to conduct PET/CT imaging for tumor
             diagnosis or staging.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnant or nursing;

          2. Severe hepatic or renal dysfunction;

          3. Low WBC (less than 3 x 10^9/L);

          4. Unable to comply with the PET/CT imaging procedures.
